reports.title: Hi there 👋
reports.query:
This is your first dashboard! 
 
You can click the (⋮) to edit this report, or add a new report to get started. You can run any Cypher query directly from each report and render data in a variety of formats. 
 
Tip: try renaming this report by editing the title text. You can also edit the page title at the top of the screen.
